     Parts of WebTV

     Names of weighty objects

     The little remote control that comes with the Internet Terminal is
     called the remote control.

     The hardware keyboard is called the remote keyboard.

     The thing that has a screen is called a television or a TV.
     The part that people stare at all day is a screen.

     Names of weightless objects

     The keyboard that appears at the bottom of the screen is called
     'the keyboard on the screen'. Remember that most of the people
     using the keyboard on the screen haven't used keyboards or
     computer screens very much, so it helps them if you describe the
     keyboard as 'the keyboard on the screen' rather than using funny
     adjectives with the word keyboard.

     Things that slide up from the bottom of the screen are called
     panels. These include the options panel, the find panel, the info
     panel the go-to panel, the save panel, and the send panel. The
     keyboard is a panel too, but it's just called the keyboard or 'the
     keyboard on the screen'.

