     We¿re great company
     We¿re the friend everyone wants to hang out with. We're fun, we're
     adventuresome, but we¿re not obscure, cutesy, wordy or terminally
     perky.

     We¿ talk to You¿
     We address the audience personally and directly. We interact with
     the viewer in the first-person plural (we) to the second person
     (you).

     We¿ are Your¿ guides. We¿re here to deliver our viewers to
     interesting and entertaining content. That is the aim of every
     word we write.

     We¿re active
     We write in the active voice. The passive voice is not used by us.

